**Warning:** This is a required internal node, removing and freeing it may cause a crash. If you wish to hide it or any of its children, use their `CanvasItem.visible` property.Adds a button with label `text` and a custom `action` to the dialog and returns the created button.
If `action` is not empty, pressing the button will emit the `custom_action` signal with the specified action string.
