essibility role description text.Sets human-readable description of the current checked state.Sets element color value.Sets element background color.Sets element foreground color.Returns the text selection in the [Input Method Editor](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Input_method) composition string, with the `Vector2i`'s `x` component being the caret position and `y` being the length of the selection.
