A custom control for editing properties that can be added to the `EditorInspector`. It is added via `EditorInspectorPlugin`.When this virtual function is called, you must update your editor.Called when the read-only status of the property is changed. It may be used to change custom controls into a read-only or modifiable state.Returns the edited property. If your editor is for a single property (added via `EditorInspectorPlugin._parse_property()`), then this will return the property.
