**Note:** This method is implemented on macOS and Windows.
**Note:** This method is not supported by macOS Dock menu items.Returns number of items in the global menu `rid`.
**Note:** This method is implemented on macOS and Windows.Return `true` is global menu is a special system menu.
**Note:** This method is implemented only on macOS.Removes the item at index `idx` from the global menu `rid`.
