**Note:** This property only has an effect on devices that support the OpenXR XR_FB_swapchain_update_state OpenGLES/Vulkan extensions.The swizzle value for the green channel of the swapchain state.
**Note:** This property only has an effect on devices that support the OpenXR XR_FB_swapchain_update_state OpenGLES/Vulkan extensions.The swizzle value for the blue channel of the swapchain state.
