Once finished with your RID, you will want to free the RID using the RenderingDevice's `free_rid()` method.Checks if the `uniform_set` is valid, i.e. is owned.Copies `size` bytes from the `src_buffer` at `src_offset` into `dst_buffer` at `dst_offset`.
