- a draw list is currently active (created by `draw_list_begin()`)
- a compute list is currently active (created by `compute_list_begin()`)Returns a copy of the data of the specified `buffer`, optionally `offset_bytes` and `size_bytes` can be set to copy only a portion of the buffer.
