If `expand` is `false`, the column will not contribute to the total ratio.Sets table column name for assistive apps.Sets color of a table cell. Separate colors for alternating rows can be specified.Sets color of a table cell border.Sets minimum and maximum size overrides for a table cell.Sets inner padding of a table cell.Adds a `cell` tag to the tag stack. Must be inside a `table` tag. See `push_table()` for details. Use `set_table_column_expand()` to set column expansion ratio, `set_cell_border_color()` to set cell border, `set_cell_row_background_color()` to set cell background, `set_cell_size_override()` to override cell size, and `set_cell_padding()` to set padding.Adds a `fgcolor` tag to the tag stack.
