**Note:** If `threaded` is enabled, this method returns a value for the loaded part of the document. Use `is_finished()` or `finished` to determine whether document is fully loaded.Returns the indexes of the first and last visible characters for the given `line`, as a `Vector2i`.
**Note:** If `visible_characters_behavior` is set to `TextServer.VC_CHARS_BEFORE_SHAPING` only visible wrapped lines are counted.
**Note:** If `threaded` is enabled, this method returns a value for the loaded part of the document. Use `is_finished()` or `finished` to determine whether document is fully loaded.Returns the number of visible lines.
