`contours`       - `PackedInt32Array`, containing indices the end points of each contour.
`orientation`    - `bool`, contour orientation. If `true`, clockwise contours must be filled.
- Two successive `CONTOUR_CURVE_TAG_ON` points indicate a line segment.
- One `CONTOUR_CURVE_TAG_OFF_CONIC` point between two `CONTOUR_CURVE_TAG_ON` points indicates a single conic (quadratic) B├®zier arc.
- Two `CONTOUR_CURVE_TAG_OFF_CUBIC` points between two `CONTOUR_CURVE_TAG_ON` points indicate a single cubic B├®zier arc.
- Two successive `CONTOUR_CURVE_TAG_OFF_CONIC` points indicate two successive conic (quadratic) B├®zier arcs with a virtual `CONTOUR_CURVE_TAG_ON` point at their middle.
