The `flip_h`, `flip_v`, and `transpose` parameters can be `true` to transform the returned polygon.Sets the occluder for the TileSet occlusion layer with index `layer_id`.Returns the occluder polygon of the tile for the TileSet occlusion layer with index `layer_id`.
