ame.Returns a terrain's name.Sets a terrain's color. This color is used for identifying the different terrains in the TileSet editor.Returns a terrain's color.Returns the navigation layers count.Adds a navigation layer to the TileSet at the given position `to_position` in the array. If `to_position` is -1, adds it at the end of the array.
